body:
SO. My dad's birthday is coming up and my mom and I want to get a dog for him and we don't know where to get one. We would have gotten one in the earlier years but my dad has anger issues and freaks out on the tiniest things until he figures out he was wrong xd. And we know he loves dogs but due to the anger issue we never got him one. And what is not the best time to get him dog than on his birthday?

My question is, what type of dog would you get? And for what reason. We are hoping to get a small dog at least.

Thanks for the help!
-Vlad
